' description: Retired archive_plan public MCP architecture boundary.
' last_updated: 2026-06-09
' ARCHIVED: archive_plan is no longer part of the public MCP registry.
@startuml archive-plan-architecture

title archive_plan — retired public MCP architecture

package "Agent Deck MCP public tools" as MCP {
  [session tools] as Session
  [worktree tools] as Worktree
  [task tools] as Task
  [issue tools] as Issue
}

package "Project / skill layer" as Project {
  [plan closeout rules] as PlanRules
  [changelog / review records] as Records
  [project archive layout] as Layout
}

package "External boundaries" as External {
  [git repository] as Git
  folder "project files" as Files
}

Session --> PlanRules : hand_off_session prompt can point to plan/tmp context
Worktree --> Git : enter_worktree / exit_worktree primitives
PlanRules --> Records
PlanRules --> Layout
Records --> Files
Layout --> Files

note bottom of MCP
  MCP exposes primitives only.
  It does not define where a project stores completed plans or records.
end note

note bottom of Project
  A skill such as project-engineering-foundation can orchestrate
  repository-specific plan/changelog/review policy outside MCP.
end note

@enduml
